<h1>React Root Error Callbacks (rootErrorHandlers)</h1>
<p>
  Exercises the global root error callbacks registered via
  <code>ReactOnRails.setOptions({ rootErrorHandlers })</code> in
  <code>spec/dummy/client/app/packs/client-bundle.ts</code> (issue #3892).
  Recorded callback events are exposed on <code>window.__ROOT_ERROR_CALLBACK_EVENTS__</code>
  for the Playwright e2e assertions.
</p>

